Any order placed for redemption or subscription directly with the AMC must be of greater than INR 25 Cr. The aforesaid threshold shall not be applicable for APs/MMs and shall be periodically reviewed. Each creation unit consists of 2,000 units of LIC MF BSE Sensex ETF. The Fund may from time to time change the size of the Creation Unit in order to equate it with marketable lots of the underlying instruments.
